* About Self dot send

Self dot send is a computing blog focusing on programming languages, software design, and technical concepts.

* About the Author

Pankaj Doharey is a software developer with interests in Emacs, Org-mode, functional programming, and system design.

* About this Blog

This blog is powered by Alchemist, a flexible blogging system for Emacs Org mode, customized with the metacritical theme.
